data.description: Welcome home to this 5 bedroom/4.5 bath on finished basement, sitting on 2.64 acres and waterfront on Toonigh Creek! The hardwood floors in the foyer greet you as you enter this beautiful property. Entertain easily with open kitchen, featuring double oven, 6 burner stove, tiled backsplash, island, and eat-in area, spacious 2-story family room with gas, ventless fireplace, and custom built-ins, formal living room with access to the front porch, formal dining room featuring a bay window and sophisticated wainscoting, and large rear deck. Relax on the recently stained screened in porch with views of the private, fenced yard. Oversized laundry room hosting tiled floors, storage, and sink, and half bath both conveniently located on the main level. The upper level features a spacious landing area with hardwood floors, built-ins, and desk. French doors lead you into the primary bedroom with trey ceiling, Berber carpet, and ensuite bath with dual closets, heated tiled floors, jetted tub, walk-in shower, and double vanities. Large secondary bedrooms feature a private bath in one and Jack-and-Jill in the others. Finished basement features an office, full bedroom and bathroom, recreation room, bar area, and flex storage space. Rest easy with newer carpet on main level and convenient central vacuum system. Plenty of room for your extra vehicles in the 3 car garage. Enjoy watching the deer on your rocking chair front porch and dream of the endless possibilities for the yard, including room for a private pool. Play in nature in the creek on your own property! This wonderful community offers tons of events for all ages! Don't miss this opportunity!
